Get feature names

Source: R/utils-classes.R
get_features.Rd

Get feature names

Usage

get_features(object, experiment = "gene")

Arguments

object

a SingleCellExperiment object

experiment

"gene" or "transcript"

Value

variable features from a SingleCellExperiment object
